### 11.3 — Dropdowns (`core/widgets/fields/drop_downs/`)

| Widget | Usage |
|--------|-------|
| `AppDropdown<T>(items, onChanged, itemAsString, label, hint)` | Full-featured dropdown with search, multi-select, loading/error states |

